Method Detail

process

void process(ImapMessage message,
             ImapProcessor.Responder responder,
             ImapSession session)
Performs processing of the command. If this processor does not understand the given message then it must return an appropriate message as per the specification. RuntimeException should not be thrown in this circumstance.

Parameters:
ImapMessage, - not null
session - ImapSession
